00:13:53,509 --> 00:13:53,870
Ah, sì.

234
00:13:54,169 --> 00:13:54,610
Buongiorno.

235
00:13:54,730 --> 00:13:55,951
Piacere, commissario Freso.

236
00:13:56,010 --> 00:13:56,510
